00:44:28.510 --> 00:44:31.270
not at the place which humans say

00:44:31.270 --> 00:44:32.670
we're obviously intending,

00:44:32.670 --> 00:44:34.080
that place over there on the floor,

00:44:34.080 --> 00:44:37.603
not this thing that I'm
using as information.

00:44:38.840 --> 00:44:41.150
And dogs seem to get this very early on

00:44:41.150 --> 00:44:43.140
given the right development.

00:44:43.140 --> 00:44:45.210
And so that's an interesting skill

00:44:45.210 --> 00:44:49.480
