00:45:07.940 --> 00:45:10.250
I think they're probably
smelling more than looking,

00:45:10.250 --> 00:45:12.020
but they're directed toward us

00:45:12.020 --> 00:45:14.410
just as in a conversation.

00:45:14.410 --> 00:45:16.900
So they really succeed at
social cognitive tasks,

00:45:16.900 --> 00:45:19.460
and the wolves are less good at that.

00:45:19.460 --> 00:45:22.273
Probably because they're less trained at,

