00:58:21.836 --> 00:58:24.010
As opposed to being attracted
to the exotic, I think,

00:58:24.010 --> 00:58:25.930
I'm kind of attracted to getting

00:58:25.930 --> 00:58:28.340
different perspectives on the ordinary.

00:58:28.340 --> 00:58:32.050
And so that's the attention
I'm interested in bringing,

00:58:32.050 --> 00:58:35.490
like a new way of looking
at something familiar.

